subject: Attention Beneficiary,
body:
Attention Beneficiary,
You have been issued a payment notice of $250 Million from the Central Bank
For your overdue payment, you are to reply with your mailing address,
Telephone/fax numbers, Bank Account details of any designated Bank of
Your choice where these funds will be transferred to.
I await the requested information ASAP.
Best regards.
INI JACKSON
+234 903 113 7038

subject: Re:   Attention Beneficiary,
body:
Hello INI JACKSON,

Wow, a million from the Central Bank! That's quite a surprise. I'm not sure how this happened, but it sounds exciting. Could you please explain more about this overdue payment? How did it come about?

Looking forward to hearing more details.

Best wishes,
Gregory
